<?xml version="1.0" encoding="UTF-8"?><song><hymn_number>42</hymn_number>
<author>Loring S. Williams</author>
<lyrics>[V1]
 Chisʋs ma! Chisʋs ma!
 Ish pi̱ nukha̱klashke;
 Pi̱ nukha̱klo pullakbano,
 E chim aiahnishke.

[V2]
 Pi̱ Shahli Chisʋs ma!
 Nana achukma ka,
 Himonasi fehna hoka.
 Ish pim atahlashke.

[V3]
 Chisʋs pi̱ Shahli ma!
 E chim ilbʋshʋshke;
 Chi Shilombish achukma yʋt
 Pim a̱ya pullashke.

[V4]
 Chim aholitopa
 Ʋba talaia ka
 Pisa pi bʋnna fehna kʋt
 Pilbʋsha fehnʋshke.
 5 Pin Chitokaka ma!
 Ish pi̱ nukha̱klo cha,
 Chi̱ hina hanta fehna ka
 Ish pi foyukashke.

[V5]
 Pi Okchalinchi ma!
 Chisʋs chi pulla ka
 Chi anukchieto hocha
 Pi yakoho̱mishke.

[V6]
 Chisʋs chia hokʋt,
 Ish pi halʋllashke,
 Okla pilbʋsha fehnʋshke.
 Pi̱ Miko Chisʋs ma!</lyrics>
<aka>Chisʋs ma!</aka>
<time_sig>S.M. (6.6.8.6.)</time_sig>
<title>Prayer to Jesus ƲIT42</title>
</song>